{"tid":498312,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"睇唔過眼 決定要話比大家知","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T16:20:19.000Z","uid":17534,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0a55430a444959ff8df82ba704f598d811c923","tid":498312,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"唔係想抹黑呢間獸醫<br />\n但諗諗下覺得佢真係好過份<br />\n<br />\n我朋友係香港註冊CFA breeder<br />\n佢有6 隻kitten 2個月 琴日晏晝去咗平時去開個間診所打第一枝疫苗 醫生仲讚佢靚女 又活潑 摸完d骨仲話好健康<br />\n返到屋企都好地地 隻隻都有行有飲水<br />\n去到半夜 突然發現到其中一隻貓奄奄一息<br />\n<br />\n咁我朋友就住住大埔  佢其實心知亦聽好多人講過呢間獸醫診所好衰 但情況危急 佢即刻帶咗貓bb去個間24 小時既獸醫診所度check<br />\n一去到 個獸醫一味淨係同佢講$2300 <br />\n又唔肯做急救 不斷講又埋單先咁 <br />\n其他在場既人都睇唔過眼<br />\n<br />\n後尾急救又閂咗道門唔比人睇<br />\n出到黎就話死咗<br />\n事後返到屋企 睇返張單 發覺d 驗血費乜費物費 左連report 都冇比過一份我個朋友<br />\n淨係一味話 同d 疫苗無關係<br />\n<br />\n返到去屋企我朋友搵到原來係有1/1000~1/5000 既機率 因為疫苗過敏而出現問題導致休克或者死亡<br />\n<br />\n但醫生完全無提及過亦都無用過抗敏針<br />\n依加我個朋友淨係覺得自己累死咗隻幼貓<br />\n如果帶佢去第二間醫院 或者有人識救 可能唔洗死<br />\nRIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab6a7c52436c9b5ce36a0b1e2c9bce86d591a16","tid":498312,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e65905ffdc4f47bcf803d23e2e1f9a08d3487c4","tid":498312,"uid":17534,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/002008_5facf68c680a38c400b266f810d4c22a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F002008_5facf68c680a38c400b266f810d4c22a.jpg&h=71b74d31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/002009_4b63626d8030d5f33356b9b4043e8cbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F002009_4b63626d8030d5f33356b9b4043e8cbc.jpg&h=6e2659c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}